; Tests for sha512.cc: SHA512 buffer handling with long input
; Covers: (SHA512_Update partial buffer fill and multi-block transform)
;         (SHA512_Final padding when buffer has residual data)
; The long payee name and deep account hierarchy ensure the hash input
; exceeds 128 bytes (one SHA512 block), forcing the transform loop.

